page.title: 07Transport
page.content: {Buses.} Red Alder Valley Buses go through Maidenhead.The first bus time is 6.14am.The last bus time is 10.30pm.It starts at Maidenhead bus station and goes to Woodlands Park and back.They come every 30 minutes on week days On Sundays they come every hour. {Trains. In our area there is a railway line.They go past every 5 minutes.The kind of trains that go past are Inter City and Inter City 125's.The Inter City 125's go to Bristol.We can hear the trains go past our school.All the trains go to London or the West country. {Air Travel.}AT White Waltham airfield there are light aircraft. They fly over the school to land. Some of the aircraft on show are World War Two fighter aircraft.
